Ex. 2¶

Изображение с водородными связями, которыми белок связывает лиганд

In [3]:
cmd.bg_color('white')
cmd.remove('solvent')
cmd.select('ligand', 'resn NAG+NDG')
cmd.hide('everything')
cmd.show_as('surface', '1LMP')
cmd.set('transparency', 0.5)
cmd.show('stick')
cmd.distance('hbo', '1LMP', 'ligand', 4, mode=2)
cmd.zoom('ligand')
cmd.png('bonds.png')
Image(filename='bonds.png', width=600, height=400)

resi = ['resi 46', 'resi 59', 'resi 103']

for r in resi:
    cmd.wizard('mutagenesis')
    cmd.get_wizard().set_mode('ALA')
    cmd.get_wizard().do_select(r)
    cmd.get_wizard().apply()
    cmd.set_wizard('done')

Получение фреймы для видео

In [12]:
cmd.mset('1 x250')
frame_nums = [1, 50, 100, 150, 200]

for fr, n in enumerate(frame_nums):
    cmd.frame(n)
    if fr < 2:
        cmd.translate([10*(-1)**fr, 10*(-1)**fr, 0], object='1lmp')
        cmd.translate([10*(-1)**(fr+1), 10*(-1)**(fr+1), 0], object='1lmp_mut')
    else:
        cmd.zoom(resi[fr-2])
    cmd.mview('store')
In [13]:
cmd.frame(250)
cmd.super('1lmp','1lmp_mut')
cmd.mview('store', object = '1lmp and 1lmp_mut')
cmd.mview('interpolate')
cmd.frame(1)

Ex. 6¶

In [23]:
phi = '90'
psi = '-190'
cmd.reinitialize()
cmd.bg_colour('white')
al = 'ALA'
cmd.fragment(al)

for i in range(2, 101):
    cmd.edit('resi %i and name C' % i)
    cmd.editor.attach_amino_acid('pk1', al)
    cmd.edit('resi %i and name Ca' % i, 'resi %i and name C' % i)
    cmd.do('torsion '+ psi)
    cmd.edit('resi %i and name N' % (i+1), 'resi %i and name Ca' % (i+1))
    cmd.do('torsion '+ phi)
cmd.edit()
cmd.zoom()

In [26]:
cmd.create('pair', 'chain A and resi 2 or chain B and resi 22')
cmd.create('nextpair', 'chain A and resi 3 or chain B and resi 23')
cmd.create('1', 'pair')
cmd.pair_fit('nextpair', 'pair')
trans = cmd.get_object_matrix('nextpair')
for x in range(2, 102):
    cmd.create(str(x), str(x-1))
    cmd.transform_selection(str(x), trans, homogenous=0)
cmd.show('sticks')
cmd.orient()
cmd.zoom()
cmd.png('g-dna.png')
Image(filename='g-dna.png', width=600, height=400)
